{"tid":1729711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際線我地唔只能單靠賣慘，要遊說令議員明白，中共過份濫用香港牟利，變相令其他國家處於不公平條件","createTime":"2019-11-17T10:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T13:16:15.000Z","uid":100155,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f1036fe6588ab9c5191a538111fee3735108b2","tid":1729711,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:29:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WTjsYR1ZUIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWTjsYR1ZUIw&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=a8c29bb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WTjsYR1ZUIw</a><br />\nStart watching from 14:32.<br />\n國際線我地唔只能單靠賣慘，要遊說令議員明白，中共過份濫用香港牟利，變相令其他國家處於不公平條件，not on the same playing field.<br />\n自從NBA事件後已經無咩推同tweet過令佢地感到受威脅ge野，例如中國可以透過香港購買航母，<strong>希望可以拋磚引玉集思廣益下</strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[將美國管制的設備透過香港空殼公司進入中國； 同埋洗錢]</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n華為藉香港向伊朗輸出技術，中共透過前港官何志平為中企行賄聯合國及非洲官員，顯示香港已經成為中共白手套。根據美方提交資料，孟晚舟擁有三本KJ字頭的特區護照，引起美國關注，港府在知情下給予三本護照，以便她掩飾行蹤及逃避出入境制裁。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭豪擲500億，用香港科學園名義引進外國頂尖大學實驗室及人員，先轉去河套區漂一漂白，再轉移至內地企業<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[利用香港執行與被制裁國家(伊朗，北韓)之貿易及石油供應。]</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n2017年年底，香港籍「方向永嘉」號輪船（Lighthouse Winmore），在公海上把油輸送給朝鮮輪船，違反聯合國安理會通過的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n2018年2月，美國公布27間受制裁的公司中，有5間是在香港註冊的船務及海運的相關公司。<br />\n<br />\n載有伊朗石油的一艘中資旗下運油貨輪(Pacific Bravo/Latin Venture)，尋求停泊香港，而港府表示不會遵從美國管制<br />\n(該油輪由中國石油天然氣集團旗下的中國昆侖銀行持有。該銀行是中國與伊朗交易的主要渠道。報道說，中國一直是伊朗石油的主要買家之一，幾乎所有買石油的費用都是透過昆侖銀行支付。)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-shipping-oil-sanctions-malaysia-exclu/exclusive-china-owned-oil-tanker-changes-name-in-apparent-effort-to-evade-u-s-sanctions-idUSKCN1V60I2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-shipping-oil-sanctions-malaysia-exclu%2Fexclusive-china-owned-oil-tanker-changes-name-in-apparent-effort-to-evade-u-s-sanctions-idUSKCN1V60I2&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=8e31744f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-shipping-oil-sanctions-malaysia-exclu%2Fexclusive-china-owned-oil-tanker-changes-name-in-apparent-effort-to-evade-u-s-sanctions-idUSKCN1V60I2&h=2a07fa2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-shipping-oil-sanctions-malaysia-exclu/exclusive-china-owned-oil-tanker-changes-name-in-apparent-effort-to-evade-u-s-sanctions-idUSKCN1V60I2</a><br />\n<br />\n過往有媒體發現有香港註冊的油輪出現在伊朗的水域附近。<br />\n<br />\n香港一間空殼公司與北韓有幾千萬美元款項紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n香港已成為中共顛覆國際商貿秩序及核心價值的白手套。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>[中國用銀彈+提供監控技術 收買小國外交 以邊緣化台灣]</strong></ins>：<br />\nChina is rapidly spreading its influence in the South Pacific by splashing cash in the countries which switch their diplomatic allegiances from Taiwan to the communist superpower：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.9news.com.au/world/60-minutes-china-staging-soft-invasion-of-south-pacific/d4078c7b-ae6a-4939-992b-ca93c15e4e1b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.9news.com.au%2Fworld%2F60-minutes-china-staging-soft-invasion-of-south-pacific%2Fd4078c7b-ae6a-4939-992b-ca93c15e4e1b&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=186de520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.9news.com.au/world/60-minutes-china-staging-soft-invasion-of-south-pacific/d4078c7b-ae6a-4939-992b-ca93c15e4e1b</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/anderscorr/status/1195897751898247170?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanderscorr%2Fstatus%2F1195897751898247170%3Fs%3D20&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=a71eefd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanderscorr%2Fstatus%2F1195897751898247170%3Fs%3D20&h=d538fc67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/anderscorr/status/1195897751898247170?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n透過一帶一路散播監控<br />\n<a href=\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/11/15/huawei-xinjiang-kazakhstan-uzbekistan-china-surveillance-state-eyes-central-asia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2019%2F11%2F15%2Fhuawei-xinjiang-kazakhstan-uzbekistan-china-surveillance-state-eyes-central-asia%2F&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=9ff941df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/11/15/huawei-xinjiang-kazakhstan-uzbekistan-china-surveillance-state-eyes-central-asia/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1195441121691865088?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1195441121691865088%3Fs%3D20&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=26823a78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1195441121691865088%3Fs%3D20&h=1d2a3db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1195441121691865088?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3WFuvz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3WFuvz.jpg&h=a154ba53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21e23e204678d3b081a75feff8387f7094d86a40","tid":1729711,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:29:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bed6f153dd80a07e034380c124669ddd2710ac05","tid":1729711,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa12e1f1a02677621cc790ef829e4b5ea00baa18","tid":1729711,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"警：大學暴徒立即離開；五毛：立即散水；林奠建制：止暴成功，票投建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c80657227c14956734eee759db1acfd75ab9331c","tid":1729711,"uid":91087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"